John M. WALSH et al., Appellants, v. BANK OF LASSEN COUNTY et al., Appellees. PATRICK WALSH & SONS, Inc., et al., Appellants, v. Mary C. HILL et al., Appellees. Nos. 6074, 6075. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. May 5, 1930.

Before BUDKIN and WILBUR, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulations of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeals dismissed.
